$ /var/log

`var/log` is the directory under which → development/log-files are typically stored.

→ Linux/fhs/var/log/wtmp records all logins and logouts

→ Linux/fhs/var/log/lastlog records when each user last logged in.

→ Linux/fhs/var/log/faillog records failed login attempts.

→ Linux/fhs/var/log/btmp records bad login attempts.


sa:

  → Linux/fhs/var/log/sudo-io

  → Linux/fhs/var/log/btmp,
  → Linux/fhs/var/log/wtmp

  → Linux/fhs/var/log/Xorg_N_log
